Non-standard packages needed to build:

doxygen:    Needed to generate HTML documentation for the source code
pkg-config: Needed to reference other libraries

OS X: Make sure /usr/local/bin is in your PATH.

	doxygen
		Download: http://ftp.stack.nl/pub/users/dimitri/doxygen-1.4.6.src.tar.gz
		./configure --prefix /usr/local
		make
		sudo make install

	pkg-config
		Download: http://pkgconfig.freedesktop.org/releases/pkg-config-0.20.tar.gz
		./configure --prefix=/usr/local
		make
		sudo make install

Linux: These packages should be available in your distribution.

Windows: Cygwin should have these packages available.
